TrustZone is it sets up two

00:08:48.210 --> 00:08:53.930
separate worlds on the core or
the multi-core device, where

00:08:53.930 --> 00:08:56.520
the two cannot communicate
except through a very well

00:08:56.520 --> 00:08:57.430
defined API.

00:08:57.430 --> 00:09:00.510
